data.description: Introducing a charming and spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home nestled in a tranquil location in East Davenport. This property exudes character and warmth, offering a serene ambiance enriched by ample natural lighting throughout. The main floor features a spacious living area perfect for entertaining with open living and dining space. The master bedroom boasts comfort and tranquility and includes a walk-in closet with full bathroom and laundry. Depending on your needs the master bedroom could be used and was previously used as a family room. There is also office space! Upstairs, a landing area provides additional versatile space, perfect for a reading nook or play area (slide can be removed).  Step outside to discover a low-maintenance patio area in the backyard with invisible fence to stay, perfect for entertaining or simply soaking up the sun. For those in need of storage, the basement offers ample space to accommodate your belongings, ensuring a clutter-free living environment. Additionally, a two-car garage provides convenience and security for your vehicles and outdoor gear. This delightful home combines comfort, functionality, and charm, offering a unique opportunity to embrace a relaxed lifestyle in a desirable location.
